{"tid":2395710,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人今日搭鐵漏低咗八達通","createTime":"2021-02-05T05:15:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T05:50:21.000Z","uid":13549,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3c2402f4a55ba091bda50cf0896bf623c79ce03e","tid":2395710,"uid":13549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T05:15:02.000Z","msg":"今日搭鐵見到有個女仔起身落車<br />\n個位有張卡<br />\n有個呀嬸望都唔望就坐咗落去<br />\n我同朋友即刻問佢係咪坐住咗張卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後追咗出去俾番個女仔<br />\n點知個女仔話張卡唔係佢嘅<br />\n咁有冇人今日搭鐵漏咗八達通呀～～～<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ac57kS6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAc57kS6.jpg&h=9690d38a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見你尋晚先啱啱增咗$100咁快唔見戥你慘呀<br />\n雖然＄200可能係小數目，但我唔見嘢都會上連登睇吓有冇人執到，當買個希望<br />\n所以希望你見到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />話我知你邊條線 大概幾點漏低 坐咩位 留低個tg啦<br />\n你唔拎番我就用咗佢㗎啦<br />\n<br />\nps 我搭鐵係我衰仔 屌細力啲"},{"pid":"81ed30120a178b0b30548fe1576e705a9da52155","tid":2395710,"uid":165339,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T05:36:47.000Z","msg":"如果係巴，故事早已結束<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"496f4658dd890c08c76dcfd60bfa5e8050a28ec0","tid":2395710,"uid":14625,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T05:39:20.000Z","msg":"執到就交去cs啦死狗公<br />\n個個都上連登咩on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ac2d4790f715126f7043858414df5fed4b101d2","tid":2395710,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"496f4658dd890c08c76dcfd60bfa5e8050a28ec0","tid":2395710,"uid":14625,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T05:39:20.000Z","msg":"執到就交去cs啦死狗公<br />\n個個都上連登咩on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T05:42:03.000Z","msg":"係啵，交完黨鐵站再開post咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb2b65e90de3ea26fc53de